    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cfd-lab-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile declaration, the credibility evidence package is accepted for the low-risk regulatory submission pathway. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; six epistemic gaps are acknowledged and documented as open items for future MRL 5 re-assessment. The Monte Carlo UQ results and bench validation at three operating points provide sufficient evidence for the current submission scope. The intended-use context is described narratively within the package description as clinical research application of the hemolysis CFD model; no structured ContextOfUse object is required under ProfileMinimal.",
